  "Description": {
    "English": "\"Glorious survivor! The <span class=\"name name-stellar\">promised star</span> will be yours!\"<br><br>A <span class=\"name name-technology\">Secure system pass</span> bearing the mark of the '<span class=\"name name-stellar\">Voice of Freedom'</span>. <br>Select the pass and use Accept Invitation (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>) to pin the location in your navigation systems.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "“光荣的幸存者！<span class=\"name name-stellar\">应许之星</span>将属于你！”<br><br>一张<span class=\"name name-technology\">安全系统通行证</span>上带着“<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自由之音</span>”的标志。<br>选择通行证并使用接受邀请（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）以在导航系统中标记位置。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "「光榮的倖存者！<span class=\"name name-stellar\">應許之星</span>將屬於你們！」<br><br>一個上面印有「<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自由之聲</span>」印記的<span class=\"name name-technology\">安全星系通行證</span>。<br>選擇通行證並使用接受邀請 (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)，在你的導航系統中釘選該地點。"
  },
